      {
        "type": "CustomEntry",
        "epId": 4781,
        "name": "芙卡洛斯",
        "desc": "<p>最後一位水神又名「正義之神」。<span class=\"wk-shady\">她爲了摧毀正義之神及其神座，並歸還水龍的力量而犧牲了自己。</span></p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2023/12/20/0c738427840832159123453a49753e8f_3478299024622747823.png",
